Class LostClientManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mapzen.android.lost.internal.LostClientManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ClientManager

    public class LostClientManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements ClientManager
    Used by LostApiClientImpl to manage connected clients and by FusedLocationProviderServiceImpl to manage client's LocationListeners, PendingIntents, and LocationCallbacks.
